						               													<description>A Zombie strategy game for 3 or more players, where the person who survives the longest wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player controls 1 Human and 3 Zombies. Aim of the game is to be the last Human to survive the Zombie attack. Each player takes turns to run from the shuffling Zombies, then each takes turns to move their Zombies to try and corner and bite the other players' Humans. Humans generally move a fixed number of 6 speaces, whilst Zombies move according to a dice roll (1-6). Get bitten as a Human and you still have 5 turns - or until you get bitten again if sooner - until you become a Zombie yourself. Cards take it beyond a basic roll 'n' move, with positive (for yourself) and negative (for others) special effects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are various cards that can either help or hinder.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
